properties.name: First Speeding Ticket
properties.description: Posted by Fiblicold spring, kyDriving with my dad when I only had a permit. Coming home from a Notre Dame football game. Was caught going 55 in a 45 (although when I was pulling over to the side, I passed the 55 sign). The officer said they were being extra careful because there were a lot of deer. Cold Spring, KY just needed the money.

properties.name: First Time Backpacking
properties.description: Posted by Fibli Camp Ottawi, VirginiaEarly years of high schoo, trying to recall exactly when... Went with my Boy Scout troop and backpacked for a week on the High Knoll Trail. Pretty great.

properties.description: Posted by FibliKiev, UkraineSpent a week in Kiev, Uk working at an orphanage. The communist influence was amazing to experience.

properties.description: Posted by Fibli Charleston, WVAt the Vandalia Festival in Charleston, WV on Memorial Day Weekend. Went to the banjo competition. Heard Cripple Creek and was hooked. I can recall leaving and telling my parents I wanted to start playing. I think this was my freshman or sophomore year in college.
